        <title type="html"><![CDATA[New themes for archlan/i3!]]></title>
        <id>04-new-themes</id>
        <link href="https://archlan.github.io/04-new-themes"/>
        <updated>2022-02-12T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<span]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>A newer interface is now shipped by default with ArchLan.</p><p>Themes have been added with the option to choose between theme, using a simple
shortcut. <code>$kyoto+v</code> (where <code>$kyoto</code> refers to "Ctrl") toggles the new ArchLan ThemeSwitch
interface that allows you to choose between a multitude of varied and colorful themes.</p><p>//
Stay updated on the development of ArchLan and chat with the project maintainer(s).</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/archlan_linux/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Instagram-%40archlan__linux-2f1254.svg?logo=instagram&amp;logoColor=white&amp;labelColor=131a1c&amp;style=for-the-badge" alt="Instagram"></a> Follow ArchLan on Instagram</li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/ArchLan_Linux" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Twitter-%40ArchLan__Linux-2f1254.svg?logo=twitter&amp;logoColor=white&amp;labelColor=131a1c&amp;style=for-the-badge" alt="Twitter"></a> Follow ArchLan on Twitter.</li><li><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/archlan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Reddit-%20r/archlan-2f1254.svg?logo=reddit&amp;labelColor=131a1c&amp;style=for-the-badge" alt="Reddit"></a> Join the official Reddit community.</li></ul>]]></content>
