        <title type="html"><![CDATA[An improved beta v0.2 is now out!]]></title>
        <id>02-beta-release</id>
        <link href="https://archlan.github.io/02-beta-release"/>
        <updated>2022-01-17T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<span]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Newer and better!
To check it out or install it on your machine, head to <a href="https://archlan.github.io/install.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ArchLan:Download</a>.</p><p>Even though there is still place for improvement, this release is much better and much more usable.</p><p>Read this post for more information about this release:</p><div class="admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"><div class="admonition-heading"><h5><span class="admonition-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="16" viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.3 5.69a.942.942 0 0 1-.28-.7c0-.28.09-.52.28-.7.19-.18.42-.28.7-.28.28 0 .52.09.7.28.18.19.28.42.28.7 0 .28-.09.52-.28.7a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3c-.28 0-.52-.11-.7-.3zM8 7.99c-.02-.25-.11-.48-.31-.69-.2-.19-.42-.3-.69-.31H6c-.27.02-.48.13-.69.31-.2.2-.3.44-.31.69h1v3c.02.27.11.5.31.69.2.2.42.31.69.31h1c.27 0 .48-.11.69-.31.2-.19.3-.42.31-.69H8V7.98v.01zM7 2.3c-3.14 0-5.7 2.54-5.7 5.68 0 3.14 2.56 5.7 5.7 5.7s5.7-2.55 5.7-5.7c0-3.15-2.56-5.69-5.7-5.69v.01zM7 .98c3.86 0 7 3.14 7 7s-3.14 7-7 7-7-3.12-7-7 3.14-7 7-7z"></path></svg></span>note</h5></div><div class="admonition-content"><p>Keep in mind that this release is a <strong>beta</strong> and I am actively developing <span style="border-radius:4px;color:#b924ff;padding:0.2rem">ArchLan</span>, which means that you might encounter bugs or unexpected errors while using it.
The next versions of ArchLan will be even better and I will make sure to
listen to users suggestion in order to make ArchLan better!</p></div></div><h2 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_R0VQ" id="release-notes">Release notes:<a class="hash-link" href="#release-notes" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><p><strong><code>January 2022 (Second Release)</code></strong></p><ul><li>Reworked the file structure of a few components</li><li>Currently remaking the i3 config</li><li>Branding official wallpapers and window manager configs</li><li>ArchLan lightdm configuration</li><li>My own zsh configuration - Undergoing maintenance</li><li>More...</li></ul><blockquote><p>This beta release provides a perfectly usable environment aimed at any type of user. The next versions will be improved over time.</p></blockquote><h2 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_R0VQ" id="latest-release">Latest release:<a class="hash-link" href="#latest-release" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><ul><li><strong><code>ISO</code></strong>: <a href="https://github.com/archlan/releases/download/v22.01/archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso</a></li><li><strong><code>SIG</code></strong>: <a href="https://github.com/archlan/releases/download/v22.01/archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso.sig" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso.sig</a></li><li><strong><code>SHA</code></strong>: <a href="https://github.com/archlan/releases/download/v22.01/archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso.sha256sum" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso.sha256sum</a></li></ul><h2 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_R0VQ" id="verify-the-authenticity-of-the-iso">Verify the authenticity of the ISO<a class="hash-link" href="#verify-the-authenticity-of-the-iso" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><ul><li>Download the <span style="border-radius:4px;color:#b924ff;padding:0.2rem"><code>ISO</code></span>, <span style="border-radius:4px;color:#b924ff;padding:0.2rem"><code>GPG signature</code></span> and the <span style="border-radius:4px;color:#b924ff;padding:0.2rem"><code>sha256sum</code></span> files</li><li>Ensure that all the files you have downloaded are present in the same directory as the ISO</li><li>Verify the key on the keyserver:</li></ul><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-bash theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx bash"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">$ gpg --recv-keys 5F765E0E531F5B53</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" class="copyButton_wuS7 clean-btn">Copy</button></div></div><ul><li>Verify the iso signature:</li></ul><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-bash theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx bash"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">$ gpg --verify archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso.sig</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" class="copyButton_wuS7 clean-btn">Copy</button></div></div><ul><li>Then verify the <code>sha256sum</code>:</li></ul><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-bash theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx bash"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">$ sha256sum -c archlan-2022.01.16-x86_64.iso.sha256sum</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" class="copyButton_wuS7 clean-btn">Copy</button></div></div>]]></content>
