        <title type="html"><![CDATA[The first beta release of ArchLan is now out!]]></title>
        <id>01-beta-release</id>
        <link href="https://archlan.github.io/01-beta-release"/>
        <updated>2022-01-05T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<span]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The first release of ArchLan is now out!
